<p>
EmacsTalk 是干啥的，是主播一时脑袋发热想出来的嘛？等等，主播是谁？</p>
<div id="outline-container-headline-1" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="headline-1">
Show Notes
</h2>
<div id="outline-text-headline-1" class="outline-text-2">
<ul>
<li>
<p><a href="https://mitpress.mit.edu/sites/default/files/sicp/index.html">Structure
and Interpretation of Computer Programs (SICP)</a></p>
</li>
<li>
<p><a href="https://www.gnu.org/software/mit-scheme/">MIT/GNU Scheme</a></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>主播最早用的配置
<a href="https://www.braveclojure.com/basic-emacs/">emacs-for-clojure</a></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>主播目前的配置 <a href="https://github.com/jiacai2050/dotfiles/tree/master/.config/emacs">.config/emacs</a>。一些用到的库</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p><a href="https://github.com/jwiegley/use-package">use-package</a>, 包安装与配置</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><a href="https://github.com/emacs-evil/evil">evil</a>，让 Emacs 拥有 VI 按键方式，释放小手指</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><a href="https://company-mode.github.io/">company</a>，代码补全</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><a href="https://github.com/emacs-lsp/lsp-mode/">lsp-mode</a> 代码跳转</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><a href="https://www.djcbsoftware.nl/code/mu/mu4e.html">mu4e</a> 邮件</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><a href="https://github.com/skeeto/elfeed">elfeed</a> RSS 阅读</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>
<p>主播博客：<a href="https://liujiacai.net/">https://liujiacai.net/</a></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>网络 ID：写代码的西瓜</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>立 flag，节目坚持做五年（即 2026-06-27）</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p>第一次录制，不足之处还望听友包涵，有任何建议欢迎留言指出，谢谢！</p>
</div>
